Bookmarks
Type "bm" to access the Firefox Bookmarks Manager.
Options
Type "opt" to access your Firefox options.
Extensions
Type "ext" to access your Firefox Extensions manager.
History
Type "hist" to access your Firefox history.
Themes
Type "theme" to access your Firefox themes.
Close tab/window
Type "x" to close a tab, or if no tabs are open, to close the window.
Downloads
Type "dl" to access your recent downloads.

Type "gmonkey" to open Greasemonkey's "Manage User Scripts" dialog.
